data.description: Property qualifies for a neighborhood grant with funds available!  Just pull up the truck because 3215 Westmont Avenue shows like a model and is move in ready.  From the spacious and open living room to the separate dining space that opens to a bright and inviting kitchen.  Just in time to prepare all your fall meals.  Freshly painted, new carpet, updated appliances, roof replaced 2020 recessed lighting unique  with a concrete parking pad in the rear, equipped with  connections for an electric vehicle. Providing 3 bedrooms with ample closet space and full bath.  Within 4 miles to Amtrak Station easy for commuting, Downtown Baltimore, Coppin State University and CCBC, University Hospital, Camden Yards and M&T Stadium, I95 easy for commuters. Seller is seeking a quick close. Call Today.
